mapproperties.key: Simulation with no symptoms attached, just the normal daily tasks are performed with no impairment.

This simulation models the problems with movement the patient has. These problems are caused by two hernias the patient has on her lower back. For these problems a filter was created that, with a probability of 0.2, makes him 150% slower on movement tasks.

This simulation models the patients pain caused by two hernias she has on her lower back. For this specific problem a filter was created that, with a probability of 0.2, makes him complain out loud about her pain.
This simulation combines both filters previously created. One makes her perform actions more slowly and the other makes her complain about her pain at random.
